<div>
    <h3 class="text-left">The Center of Attention</h3>
    <p>With each aerial flight project, we create several core operational datasets referred to as planimetric data.
        These are things like building footprints, streets, sidewalks, recreation areas, bridges, curbs, hydrography
        and on and on and on.
        <br>
        We make it all freely accessible on <a href="http://opendata.dc.gov">Open Data DC</a> as owners of this data and
        imagery. It is one of the DC GIS programâ€™s largest bi-annual projects and certainly seems like the center of
        attention.<br><br></p>
    <a target="_blank" href=http://opendata.dc.gov/datasets?q=planimetric class="btn btn-default open-btn">View all
        Planimetric Data</a>
</div>
